<div class="ttpost">
	<div class="ttmeta-more">
		<a name="c1484" href="#c1484">#</a>
		Posted on <strong>16 September 2008</strong> at <strong>08:34 AM</strong>
	</div>
	<p>@touranaga - It should save them in whatever folder you ran wget from.
</p>
<p>So if you just opened up a terminal and did it straight from there, they should be in your home folder, under a directory of the website address (for example /home/yourname/fosswire.com).
</p>
<p>If you moved into a different directory with cd, then the mirrors will be placed there.
</p>
	<br class="clear" />
